1) install smbclient and cifs-utils

sudo apt-get install smbclient cifs-utils

2) edit /etc/fstab according to example from fstab.example

3) check that backup.sh has executable permission

4) run crontab -e and add into them next job - run bacjup script every day at 0:0am

0 0 * * *       /home/kamil/.local/settings/nix/backup/backup.sh